  "body": "### Describe the feature\n\nThe current version of hardhat-viem doesn't support library linking in its `deployContract` and `sendDeploymentTransaction` methods. The API should mirror the approach taken by `hardhat-ethers` for library linking, as outlined [here](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@nomicfoundation/hardhat-ethers#library-linking). A proper error should be displayed if a contract is deployed with an unlinked library.\n\n### Search terms\n\nhardhat-viem viem linking library",
